reviewText: Dr Prozak is laugh out loud funny before you are ready for it. The human condition is highlighted in resourceful and meaningful ways while the tone keeps it firmly grounded in dark comedy. You shouldn't miss this..

If you are upset because the movie has no point, you are missing the point of the movie. Just watch it, listen to the disclaimers, and when it's over, stop watching it. It doesn't warrant anyone, ever, getting offended (unless you are missing the point I guess). This type of movie takes a different kind of viewer, LIKE ME.

This Movie was cleverly done. I was so entertained from start to finish. It will definitely make you laugh with its dry antics during the radio show. Listening to this "Anti-Advice" from this radio host was side-splitting. The random things that occur throughout the movie also adds interest as well. You won't be disappointed in Dr. Prozak's in his dysfunctional self-help advice...!

From start to finish this movie kept me laughing.  One thing after another!
I would recommend to anyone who has a great sense of humor and wants a movie to sit around with your friends and laugh your ass off!
Trash.  Should get zero stars.  No quality whatsoever.
laughed so hard I pissed my pants ..
Funniest DVD I have watched in a long time!  I watched it again because I was laughing so hard I missed parts of it!  Would translate well into a play! Great work, Bob!
This is a very fun movie. Dr Prozak is that person inside all of us that wants to shout, what were you thinking,  when faced with stupidity. A must see movie.
You will laugh until you cry! I could watch it over and over! Great work!
